{"tid":931541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日華為，明日DJI同一眾航拍公司","createTime":"2018-12-07T06:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T09:00:22.000Z","uid":9348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc53f9c027540a52de51f4b1a848a4ce675fc06","tid":931541,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b46dc8d112618bddc474f4e0f0e63164cec926","tid":931541,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"小米, VIVO"},{"pid":"a17ef01ba95849eb536fa9934256494b0c4a4a0a","tid":931541,"uid":53735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"DJI 是十分可能已被CIA釘上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港 DJI 航拍集體禁飛　習總訪港 官方直接鎖你機<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/06/29/djinfz/life-tech/drone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2Fdjinfz%2Flife-tech%2Fdrone%2F&d=rwHUzJFazYqurwARpf8t4P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=54e7c543\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/06/29/djinfz/life-tech/drone/</a><br />\nDJI特殊禁飛區Q&amp;A<br />\n1. 於新成立的特殊禁飛區內，DJI航拍機起飛會如何？<br />\n經過DJI GO App操作的DJI航拍機，一律都會不能起飛，亦即是封鎖了飛行能力。<br />\n<br />\n2. 於非特殊禁飛區內成功起飛後，如進入特殊禁飛區，又會如何？<br />\n經過DJI GO App操作的DJI航拍機，若飛行時接近特殊禁飛區，航拍機會不能再向禁飛區方向飛行，只會定在原位，用家可以自行將航拍機返回起飛地點。<br />\n<br />\n3. 圖傳性能會受到影響嗎？<br />\n不會影響的，圖傳性能都會如常。<br />\n<br />\n4. DJI什麼機種會受影響？<br />\nPhantom系列包括Phantom 3及Phantom4系列、Inspire 1及2系列，Mavic Pro，Spark，即所有經過DJI GO而操作的航拍機都會受到限制。<br />\n<br />\n5. 特殊禁飛區會至到何時呢？<br />\n我們是根據香港民航署的指引而設立，所以特殊禁飛區的時限也是由6 月 29 日上午 9 時至 7 月 1 日下午 6 時為止。"},{"pid":"ea440bbd93e1eeab081853f96e8c5e1dfa7f1e17","tid":931541,"uid":90704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"之前唔係搞過佢黎咩？"}]}